\id 1JN - Projet Kiyaka
\toc3 1Yo
\toc2 Watheti wa Yowani
\toc1 Mukanda wa theti wa Yowani
\mt2 Mukanda wa theti wa Yowani
\mt1 1Yowani
\imt1 Khotidi ya mukanda
\ip Mikanda mitatu mya Bulunda bwa Pha mizayakani hanga mikanda mya Yowani. Wa theti muna mikanda mitatu meni myamina wubatiku songila keti zina dya musoniki. Musoniki wa mukanda wa zodi yi wuna wa tatu kabati monika hanga «mbuta». Kabatiwa sonikina mutwadisi mosi wa Dibundu, wuna bisi zitisa kwena batu.
\ip Mukanda wa theti wubatiku songila keti nati kabati sonikina. Mukanda wa zodi, kwena «Mukhetu wuna kásola Nzambi yi kwena bana bandi», kabatiwa sonikina, disongidila ni kwena kimvuka kya bakidisitu yi kwena batu bandi. Mukanda wa tatu kabatiwa sonikina mukidisitu wuna bisi tela ni Kayusi. Yandu yandu kenina mukwa dingumba dimosi dina dyenina yi mambu hana kati dya bakidisitu. Mikanda mitatu meni myami báhitikamya kwena mangumba mana matomi zaya musamu wa bukheti kásonika Yowani.
\ip Tangwa lawu dyahita tuka buna básamwana musamu wa Yesu Kidisitu mu mbala ya theti. Bakidisitu babana babati tanga musamu wa bukheti wa Yowani babatiku tambwasa mutindu wa kubakisila musamu wandi. Batu bahika bálubuka mu mangumba ma bawu. Bahika babati kotisa mvwalangani hakati dya bimvuka. Babatiku kwikila ni Kidisitu kalenda kwisila mu kimutu. Amana beku yi mupfunu wa Yesu: lufwa yi lufutumuku lwandi byeku mupfunu kikuma kya bawu. Babati zimbula: «Thweku yi masumu», «Tumuzayini Nzambi», «Mu mwini thwenina kaasi luzingu lwa bawu lubati songila mambu mahika». Kaasi luzingu lwa bawu lubati songila mambu mahika.
\ip Musoniki wa mikanda mya Yowani kabati lomba kwena bakidisitu ni balandaku malongi ma mbi mana matadidini Yesu yi Nzambi. Bana ba Nzambi bisi kwikila ni Yesu Kidisitu wisa kyedika mu kimutu. Babana bisi bindika mambu mandi benina batendi ba Kidisitu. Bakwikidi bafweti kala kwikama ku musamu wuna báyuka tuka ku luyandiku. Musamu meni wuna wubatibwa tambwasa: kuzola Nzambi yi Yesu, kwenina kuzola bakwenu. Bulungi ni ndyatidi ya bakidisitu yafwanakana yi mambu mamana bisi kwikila.
\c 1
\s1 Ndinga ya luzingu
\p 
\v 1 Mamana mákala tuka ku luyandiku, mamana twáyuka, mamana twámona yi mesu metu, mamana twátala, amana moku metu masimbini; yi yawu Ndinga yisi hana luzingu\f a \fr 1:1 \ft Kufwanikisa yi nzila ya 2:13; Ywn 1:1. \f*.
\v 2 Mukuma luzingu meni luna lwámonika, thwisilwa tila kimbangi amana tulusamwanilwa luzingu lwa mvula yi mvula, luna lwakala kwena Tata amana lwisa monika kwena betu\f b \fr 1:2 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Ywn 1:14. \f*
\v 3 mamana twámona yi mamana twáyuka, tulusamwanima benu phi ndangu lwakala phi mu kithwadi yi betu. Kinga kithwadi kyetu kyenina yi Tata amana hakimosi yi Mwana wandi, Yesu Kidisitu.
\v 4 Amana, betu, tusonikima, ndangu kyesi kyetu kyakala kyalungila.
\s1 Nzambi kenina mwini
\p 
\v 5 Musamu wuna twáyuka kwena yandi amana tulusamwani: Nzambi kenina mwini, amana mwena yandi mwisiku kala keti mudima.
\v 6 Ho twazonza ni twenina mu kithwadi yi yandi, kuna yi kudyatilaka muna mudima, bingumba thwenina amana tusadiku mana menina kyedika.
\v 7 Kaasi yuka ni tubati dyatila mu mwini bwosu kenina yandi meni mu mwini, hana mu kithwadi thwenina betu yi betu, amana menga ma Yesu, Mwana wandi, mabati tusemisa muna masumu moosu.
\p 
\v 8 Yuka twazonza ni tweku yi masumu, tutoti betu betu, amana kyedika kyeninamwoku mwena betu.
\v 9 Kaasi yuka ni twafunguna masumu metu, yandi kenina masonga amana walunga: katúlolula masumu amana katúsemisa mu kukonda kwa masonga\f d \fr 1:9 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Mkg 32:1-5.\f*.
\v 10 Yuka twazonza ni tuhodiku masumu, tumukwati kingumba, amana ndinga yandi yeninamwoku mwena betu.
\c 2
\s1 Kidisitu wisi tuyakidila
\p 
\v 1 Bana bama, mbati lusonikina bwabuna ndangu lusumukaku. Kaasi yuka ni mutu wusumukini, thwenina yi Nganzi mosi ku mbela ya Tata, Yesu Kidisitu, yandi wenina mukwa masonga.
\v 2 Yandi meni wisa ditambika hanga kimenga kikuma kya ndoluka ya masumu metu\f a \fr 2:2 \ft ...masumu metu: kufwanikisa yi Lom 3:25-26. \f*; ka masumu ma betu lwesi ku, kaasi yi masumu ma tsi yosu.
\p 
\v 3 Muna mutindu meni wawuna thwisi muzayila; yuka ni twalundaka mikuku myandi.
\v 4 Yuka mutu kazimbulaka: «Yimuzayini», kaasi kisiku lunda mikuku myandi, kingumba kenina, amana mwena yandi mwakonda kyedika.
\v 5 Kaasi wuna wisi lunda Ndinga yandi, mu kyedika, lungongu lwa Nzambi lwenina mwena yandi. Muna bwabuna, twalenda zayila ni mwena yandi thwenina.
\v 6 Wuna wisi zonza ni mwena yandi kisi nangina, kafweti dyatila bwosu buna kádyatila yandi.
\s1 Mukuku wa pha
\p 
\v 7 Baphangi batondama, heku ni mukuku wa pha yilusonikini, kaasi mukuku wa khulu, wawuna lwátambula tuka mu luyandiku; mukuku meni wawuna wa khulu, wenina ndinga yina lwatekila yuka\f b \fr 2:7 \ft Tala muna Ywn 13:34.\f*.
\v 8 Kinga, mukuku wa pha mbati lusonikina; kyedika kina kyenina mwena Yandi, kyenina phi mwena benu. Kikuma, phipha yibati kwenda amana mwini wa kyedika wutwi kedi.
\p 
\v 9 Wuna wisi zimbula ni mu mwini kenina kuna yi kumengaka phangi wandi, yanduna, mu phipha kenina.
\v 10 Wuna wisi tonda phangi wandi, mu mwini kisi nangina, amana mwena yandi, mwakonda kisinza kya kubwila.
\v 11 Kaasi wuna wisi menga phangi wandi, yanduna, mu phipha kenina; mu phipha kisi dyatila amana kazayikwoku kuna kisi kwenda kikuma phipha yamufidinga mesu.
\p 
\v 12 Mbati lusonikina, bana bama kikuma masumu menu maloluki kikuma kya zina dya Yandi.
\v 13 Mbati lusonikina batata, kikuma lumuzayini wuna wisi kala tuka ku luyandiku. Mbati lusonikina, bandumba yi masanda, kikuma lwámununga kiphidi-mutu.
\p 
\v 14 Yilusonikini, bana bama, kikuma lumuzayini Tata. Yilusonikinini, batata, kikuma lumuzayini Wuna wisi kala tuka ku luyandiku. Yilusonikinini bangunza, kikuma lwenina yi ngolu, ndinga ya Nzambi yisi zingila mwena benu amana benu lwámununga kiphidi-mutu.
\p 
\v 15 Luzolaku tsi, keti bima bina byenina mu tsi. Yuka ni mutu wisi zola tsi, lungongu lwa Tata lweninamwoku mwena yandi;
\v 16 mukuma, kyosu kina kyenina mu tsi: nzoluka ya lutu, nzoluka ya mesu amana bwabuna nzoluka ya kulumbika bima bya ha tsi. Byabina byosu byisiku tuka kwena Tata, kaasi bima bya ha tsi.
\v 17 Kinga tsi yibati hita, yi nzoluka yandi phi; kaasi wuna wisi hanga luzolu lwa Nzambi kisi zinga mu kimakulu.
\s1 Mutendi wa Kidisitu
\p 
\v 18 Bana bama, dyekina tangwa dya tsuka; lwáyuka kuzonzila ni mutendi wa Kidisitu kabati kwisa, amana henina yi lawu dya batendi ba Kidisitu: bwabuna tuzayidi ni dyadi tangwa dya tsuka\f d \fr 2:18 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Mth 24:5,23-24; Mlk 13:21-22.\f*.
\v 19 Kwena betu bálubwakila, kaasi bákalaku ba betu; mukuma, wadi ni bákala ba betu, wadi bakhana zingila hakimosi yi betu; kaasi muna bwabuna, bubati monika ni ka mosi ku wa bawu wenina wa betu.
\p 
\v 20 Benu bátomika kwena Kitembu Kyatoma, benu boosu luzayi.
\v 21 Yuka ni mbati lusonikina, heku ni kikuma luzayiku kyedika, kaasi kikuma luzayikya, kikuma phi kya buna ni ka bukamvi bumosi ku butukini ku kyedika.
\p 
\v 22 Amana nati wenina kingumba? Yuka ni ka wuna ku wisi suwangana ni Yesu kenina Kidisitu. Yandi wuna mutendi wa Kidisitu: yandi kisi suwangana, muna mbala mosi, yi Tata yi Mwana.
\v 23 Wosu wuna wamusuwangana Mwana, yandi keku phi yi Tata; wuna wisi tambwasa Mwana kenina phi yi Tata\f e \fr 2:23 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Mth 11:27; Ywn 5:23; 15:23.\f*.
\p 
\v 24 Kwena benu, yambula mana lwáyuka tuka ku luyandiku mazingila mwena benu. Yuka ni mana lwáyuka tuka ku luyandiku mananginaka mwena benu, lwanángina, benu phi, mwena Mwana yi mwena Tata.
\v 25 Amana kilangi kátusila yandi, kyenina kya luzingu lwa mvula yi mvula.
\p 
\v 26 Yilusonikinini bwabuna, kikuma kya mana matadidini batu bana bisi lutotisa.
\v 27 Kwena benu bátomika kwena Kitembu Kyatoma, lweku yi mupfunu ni mutu kalulonga; kaasi bwosu buna Kitembu Kyatoma kálulongila muna mambu moosu, kyedika kálulonga, kálulonga bukamvi. Yi hakana ni hangenu mana kálulonga: nanginakenu hakimosi mwena Yandi.
\p 
\v 28 Amana buthwena bwabu, bana bama, nanginakenu hakimosi mwena Kidisitu, ndangu twakala babasa yi kikumbwala tangwa kakwisa monika amana tukwatukaku tsoni ku thwala ya yandi mu kilumbu kya kukwisa kwandi.
\v 29 Yuka lwazaya ni mukwa masonga kenina, zayenu ni wosu wuna wenina yi masonga mwena Nzambi kábutukila.
\c 3
\s1 Bana ba Nzambi
\p 
\v 1 Tala mutindu wa kuzola kuna kátuzola Tata! Lungongu lwandi lwenina muna mutindu wuna bisi tutedila betu bana ba Nzambi. Hahana tsi yikondi tuzayila: Tsi yámuzayaku Nzambi\f a \fr 3:1 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Ywn 1:12.\f*.
\v 2 Banduku bama, buthwena, thwekina bana ba Nzambi, amana buna twakwisa kala khaniku kedi buzayakana; kaasi tuzayi ni kosu tangwa dina kakwisa dimonikisa, twafwánakana yi yandi, kikuma twamúmona bwosu buna kenina.
\v 3 Wosu wuna wasya kivuvu kya mutindu wuna mwena yandi-meni, wudisemisini, bwosu buna kenina yandi-meni wa kasemi.
\p 
\v 4 Wosu wuna wisi sumuka, mutsiku kisi tendisa, mukuma disumu dyenina kutendisa mutsiku.
\v 5 Luzayibwa ni Yesu Kidisitu kísila kikuma kya kukatula masumu amana mwena yandi, mwakonda disumu.
\v 6 Yi hakana ni, wosu wuna wanangina mwena yandi kisiku sumuka. Wosu wuna wusumukini, kisi songila ni kámumonaku, kámuzayaku phi.
\p 
\v 7 Bana bama, ka mutu ku kalutotisa! Wuna wisi hanga mambu ma masonga kenina yandi meni mukwa masonga, bwosu buna kenina yandi meni Kidisitu mukwa masonga.
\v 8 Wuna wisi landa mu kuhola disumu kenina wa kiphidi-mutu, mukuma kiphidi-mutu wásumuka tuka ku luyandiku. Mwana wa Nzambi kísila lwesi kikuma kya kuzanga mihangu mya kiphidi-mutu.
\p 
\v 9 Wosu wuna wábutuka mwena Nzambi wáyambula mu kuhola disumu, mukuma mbutu ya Nzambi yenina mwena yandi; bwosu buna Nzambi kenina Tata wandi, kafwaniku hika ni kasumuka.
\v 10 Tala mana misi baswaswanisa bana ba Nzambi yi bana ba kiphidi-mutu: wosu wuna wisiku hanga mambu ma masonga, kondilo kisiku zola phangi wandi, keku wa Nzambi.
\s1 Kudizola benu yi benu
\p 
\v 11 Kikuma, tala musamu wuna lwáyuka tuka ku luyandiku: tudizolenu betu yi betu\f b \fr 3:11 \ft Tala muna Ywn 13:34.\f*.
\v 12 Tukalaku hanga Kayina: kákala wa kiphidi-mutu amana wáhonda myaki wandi. Amana biki kámuhondila? Kikuma mihangu mya Kayina mbi myákala, kinga mina mya myaki wandi mya masonga myákala\f d \fr 3:12 \ft Tala muna Kuy 4:1-8. -kákala wa kiphidi-mutu: kondilo, kwena kiphidi-mutu kakala yekamina. \f*.
\p 
\v 13 Luyitukaku, baphangi, yuka ni batu ba tsi yayi balumenga\f e \fr 3:13 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Luk 6:22; Ywn 15:18-19; 17:14.\f*.
\v 14 Betu tuzayi ni twáhitila tuka ku lufwa yi kuna luzingu; kikuma thwisi bazola baphangi. Wuna wisiku zola, mu lufwa kisi nangina\f f \fr 3:14 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Ywn 5:24.\f*.
\v 15 Wosu wuna wayúkila phangi wandi kikudi-kudi, yandi kenina mukwa khengu. Kinga luzayibwa ni heku keti mukwa khengu mosi wenina yi kifulu kya kunangina muna luzingu lwa mvula yi mvula mwena yandi-meni.
\v 16 Tala buna thwisi zayila lungongu: Yesu Kidisitu wálambula luzingu lwandi kikuma kya betu. Betu phi, tufweti lambula luzingu lwetu kikuma kya baphangi betu.
\v 17 Yuka ni mutu wenina yi kuvwa kwa ha tsi kamona phangi wandi wuna wenina yi mupfunu wa kima kaasi wumukasidi mbundu, abweti lungongu lwa Nzambi fwani lwanangina mwena yandi\f h \fr 3:17 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Klg 15:7-8. \f*?
\v 18 Bana bama, tuzodilaku lwesi ha lebu yi lengu ndinga kaasi mu mihangu yi kyedika.
\s1 Kikumbwala ku thwala ya Nzambi
\p 
\v 19 Tala buna twazáyila ni ku kyedika thwisi yekamina. Bwabuna mbundu yetu yalenda diyuka ni yalunga yenina ku thwala ya Nzambi.
\v 20 Kikuma, ata mbundu yetu yituhekini kibela, tuzayini ni Nzambi wa mbuta kenina kuhita mbundu yetu amana yandi wuzayini moosu.
\v 21 Amana banduku bama, yuka ni mbundu yetu yituhekiku kibela, twalenda kala babasa yi kikumbwala ku thwala ya Nzambi.
\v 22 Thwisi tambula kwena yandi byosu bina thwisi lomba, kikuma thwisi lemvuka ku mikuku myandi amana thwisi hanga mana misi musephidisa yandi.
\v 23 Tala mukuku wandi: bulungi twakwikila muna khumbu ya Mwana wandi Yesu Kidisitu amana phi twazolana betu betu, bwosu buna wenina mukuku wandi\f i \fr 3:23 \ft Tala muna Ywn 13:34; 15:12,17.\f*.
\v 24 Wuna wisi lunda mikuku mya Yandi kisi nangina mu kithwadi yi Nzambi amana yandi Nzambi muna kenina mwena yandi. Tala buna thwisi zayila ni Nzambi muna kenina mwena betu: muna lusadisu lwa Kitembu wuna kátuheka
\c 4
\s1 Kitembu kya Nzambi yi kitembu kya Mutendi
\p 
\v 1 Baphangi batondama, lukwikilakaku mwena kosu kitembu; kaasi simbululakenu bitembu mu zayila yuka ni byenina bya Nzambi, mukuma bambikudi ba bukamvi lawu bamwangani mu tsi.\f a \fr 4:1 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Klg 13:2-6. \f*
\v 2 Tala buna lwazayila yuka ni Kitembu kya Nzambi wuna: kitembu kyosu kina kyatámbwasa ni Yesu Kidisitu kisa mu kimutu kyakina kyenina kya Nzambi.
\v 3 Kaasi wosu wuna wubwisini mu kutambwasa Yesu bwosu buna kenina, yandi keku wa Nzambi, kaasi kenina kitembu kya Mutendi wa Kidisitu: lwáyuka ni wuna wáfwana mu kukwisa amana buthwena wekina kedi muna tsi.
\p 
\v 4 Kaasi benu, bana bama, Nzambi wuluvwini amana phi lwábanunga bambikudi ba bukamvi; mukuma Wuna wenina mwena benu kenina wa mbuta kuhita wuna wenina mwena babana bavwini kwena tsi.
\v 5 Batu meni babana, tsi yibavwini. Yihakana ni nzonzidi ya bawu yenina ya mutindu wa batu ba tsi amana tsi yisi bayukila.
\v 6 Kaasi betu, Nzambi wutuvwini. Mutu wuna wumuzayini Nzambi kisi tuyukila; wuna kondi kala wa Nzambi kisiku tuyukila. Bwabuna twalenda zayila Kitembu wa kyedika yi kitembu kina kyisi totisa.
\s1 Nzambi kenina lungongu
\p 
\v 7 Banduku bama batondama, tudizolenu betu yi betu, mukuma lungongu kwena Nzambi lwisi tuka. Wosu wuna wisi zola mukwenu, mwena Nzambi kábutukila amana phi wumuzayi Nzambi.
\v 8 Wuna wisiku zola kábutukilaku mwena Nzambi, mukuma Nzambi kenina lungongu.
\v 9 Tala Nzambi buna kásongila lungongu lwandi kikuma kya betu: Yandi wátuma Mwana wandi mosi muna tsi, mu twavwila luzingu lwa mwana Yandi\f b \fr 4:9 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Ywn 3:16.\f*.
\v 10 Amana lungongu meni lwaluna lwenina bwabu: heku ni betu twámuzola Nzambi, kaasi yandi wátuzola; wátuma Mwana wandi wuna wádilambula hanga kimenga kikuma kya ndoluka ya masumu metu\f d \fr 4:10 \ft Tala muna 2:2. \f*.
\p 
\v 11 Banduku bama, yuka ni bwabuna kátuzodila Nzambi, tufweti dizola phi betu yi betu.
\v 12 Heku mutu wámumona kedi Nzambi. Yuka ni twadizolaka betu yi betu, Nzambi kenina mwena betu, amana lungongu lwandi lwisi lungidila mwena betu\f e \fr 4:12 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Ywn 1:18. \f*.
\p 
\v 13 Muna bwabuna, tuzayi ni mwena yandi thwisi nangina, hanga yandi mwena betu: yandi wátuheka Kitembu wandi.
\v 14 Amana betu, twámona amana tubati ta kimbangi ni Tata kámuhitika Mwana wandi hanga Muhuludi wa tsi\f f \fr 4:14 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Ywn 3:17; 4:42. \f*.
\v 15 Wuna wisi tambwasa ni Yesu kenina Mwana wa Nzambi, Nzambi kisi nangina mwena yandi, bwosu yandi mwena Nzambi.
\v 16 Amana betu, tuzayilwa lungongu luna kenina lwawu Nzambi kikuma kya betu, amana thwisi kwikila ni Nzambi kisi tuzola.
\p Nzambi kenina lungongu; wuna wisi nangina mu lungongu, mwena Nzambi kisi nangina, amana Nzambi kisi nangina mwena yandi.
\v 17 Yuka ni lungongu lwakala lwalungila mwena betu, hahana nana twakádila babasa yi kikumbwala muna kilumbu kya pfundusu; bwosu buna kenina Yandi, bwabuna thwenina betu phi mu tsi yayi.
\v 18 Muna lungongu mwisiku kala yi bweya; lungongu lwa mukwandi lwisi katula bweya. Bweya bwádikasa yi kuhingila kwa ndola amana wuna wenina yi bweya keku walungila muna lungongu.
\p 
\v 19 Kwena betu, thwisi zola, kikuma yandi wátekila tuzola mutu wa theti.
\v 20 Yuka ni mutu kazonzaka: «Nzambi yisi muzola» amana kamengaka phangi wandi, kenina kingumba. Kikuma, yuka ni kisiku muzola phangi wandi yandi kisi mona, kalendaku muzola phi Nzambi wuna kisiku mona.
\v 21 Amana tala mukuku kátuheka: wuna wisi zola Nzambi kafweti zola phi phangi wandi\f h \fr 4:21 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Mth 22:36-40; Mlk 12:28-31; Luk 10:25-28. \f*.
\c 5
\s1 Kinunga kyetu ha thandu ya tsi
\p 
\v 1 Wosu wuna wukwikidini ni Yesu kenina Kidisitu wuna wábutuka mwena Nzambi, amana wosu wuna wisi buta, kisi muzola phi wuna wubutukini mwena Nzambi.
\v 2 Muna mambu meni mamana, tuzayi ni thwisi bazola bana ba Nzambi: tangwa thwisi muzola Nzambi amana thwisi sadila bwosu buna myenina mikuku myandi.
\v 3 Mukuma lungongu lwa Nzambi, lwenina ni twalunda mikuku myandi. Amana mikuku myandi myeku phasi\f a \fr 5:3 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Ywn 14:15. \f*,
\v 4 kikuma kyosu kina kyábutukila mwena Nzambi kyenina yi kinunga mu mambu matadidini tsi; amana kinunga kina kyánunga tsi, kyenina lukwikilu lwetu.
\v 5 Nati wánunga tsi? Yuka ni ka wuna ku lwesi wisi kwikila ni Yesu kenina Mwana wa Nzambi.
\s1 Kimbangi kina báta kikuma kya Yesu Kidisitu
\p 
\v 6 Yandi, Yesu Kidisitu, wisila muna mamba yi menga; heku ni mu mamba lwesi, kaasi yi mamba yi menga; amana Kitembu wisi ta kimbangi, kikuma Kitembu kenina kyedika.
\v 7 Mukuma bambangi batatu benina\f b \fr 5:7 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Klg 19:15. \f*:
\v 8 Kitembu, mamba yi menga, amana bawu boosu benina yi kimbangi kimosi.
\v 9 Yuka ni twatambwasaka kimbangi kya batu, kimbangi kya Nzambi kihitini mu kutoka; mukuma kimbangi kya Nzambi kyenina ni kata kimbangi kikuma kya Mwana wandi.
\v 10 Wuna wisi sya lukwikilu lwandi mwena Mwana wa Nzambi kenina yi kimbangi muna mbundu ya yandi meni; wuna wisiku kwikila, kingumba kisi mukitula Nzambi, kikuma kya buna kakondi kwikila mu kimbangi kina kata Nzambi kikuma kya Mwana wandi.
\v 11 Kimbangi meni kina kyenina bwabu: Nzambi wátuheka luzingu lwa mvula yi mvula amana luzingu meni luna, lwenina mwena Mwana wandi.
\v 12 Wuna wenina yi Mwana, luzingu kenina lwawu; kaasi wuna wukondi kala yi Mwana wa Nzambi wukondi luzingu\f d \fr 5:12 \ft Kufwanikisa yi Ywn 3:36. \f*.
\s1 Luzingu lwa mvula yi mvula
\p 
\v 13 Yilusonikinini mambu mana ndangu lwazaya ni luzingu lwa mvula yi mvula lwenina lwawu benu babana lwisi kwikila mu zina dya Mwana wa Nzambi.
\v 14 Kikumbwala kina thwenina kyawu ku thwala ya yandi kyenina ni yuka twalomba kyosu kina mu luzolu lwa yandi, kisi tuyukila.
\v 15 Amana yuka thwisi kumbwala ni kisi tuyukila, muna moosu mana twálomba kedi, tuzayi phi ni tutambudima kedi.
\p 
\v 16 Yuka ni mutu wumoni ni phangi wandi, disumu kahodini dina dyisiku nata ku lufwa, bulungini kasambila amana Nzambi kahána luzingu kwena phangi meni wuna. Mambu mama matadidini batu babana bisi hola masumu mana misiku nata ku lufwa. Kaasi henina yi disumu dimosi dyisi nata ku lufwa, amana heku ni kikuma kya disumu dya mutindu wuna ndobidi mu kusambila.
\v 17 Kukonda kwa masonga kwosu kwenina disumu amana henina yi disumu dimosi dina dyisiku nata ku lufwa.
\p 
\v 18 Tuzayi ni wosu wuna wábutukila mwena Nzambi kisiku hola disumu; mukuma Mwana wa Nzambi kisi mutala amana kiphidi-mutu kamúhangaku kima.
\p 
\v 19 Tuzayibwa ni bana ba Nzambi thwenina amana ni tsi ya muthu yenina mu luyalu lwa kiphidi-mutu.
\p 
\v 20 Kaasi tuzayi phi ni Mwana wa Nzambi wisa amana wátuheka ngangu zina zisi tusadisa mu kuzayila Wuna wenina wa kyedika. Thwisi nangina ha kimosi kwena Wuna wenina wa kyedika mwena Mwana wandi Yesu Kidisitu. Yandi Nzambi wa kyedika, yandi luzingu lwa mvula yi mvula.
\p 
\v 21 Bana bama, dikengenu ku nzambi za biteki!
